{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_14", "eventName": "慈悲燈塔", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "14-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "確認交戰視界", "storyInfo": "W聽到了特蕾西婭留下的殘響，終於認清了特蕾西婭走向眾魂的事實。她放下了心理負擔，做好了真正面對特蕾西婭的準備。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wild_a", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.7, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找到你了。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瘋子……你和他們說的一樣，是瘋子。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確實很了解我。那麼，你一定知道落到我手裡的人都是什麼下場。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#9$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說吧，你們在卡茲戴爾附近還有什麼部署？這場過於簡單的戰鬥背後到底藏著什麼秘密？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#10$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算我懶得弄清楚特雷西斯扔下卡茲戴爾這事裡頭有什麼不可告人，但也別把我當白癡。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#10$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也沒能擺脫我的巫術，你以為你還能撐多久？", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "撐到你跪地求饒，把該交代的都交代出來為止。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#9$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傭兵啊……", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得自己總能活下來……每個人在死前都是這麼以為的。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人會是被死亡遺忘的寵兒，眾魂等著呢，你逃不掉，她也逃不掉……你們都是徒勞。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你呢？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#11$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我？我願意退場。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽好了，薩卡茲，與軟弱告別吧。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新的時代已經來了，那才是屬於我們的時代。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕，那個“我們”之中，已經沒有我的存在。", "name": "薩卡茲戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$grenade_explosion", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$blooddrop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#2$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W！你剛剛——你的手……醫療幹員，這裡需要緊急處理！", "name": "巴別塔小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽的，這傢伙主動引爆了手榴彈。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泥沼終於消退，腐爛的氣味被強風吹散。可眼前的這片荒野，卻為何還是這麼昏暗？"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不安的感覺越來越強烈。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些薩卡茲戰士死前的表情，可稱得上是……虔誠。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的表情，怎麼會出現在他們那種人臉上？"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，聯繫上本艦了嗎？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小隊之間的通訊恢復了一部分。", "name": "巴別塔小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，與本艦的通訊至今還有干擾，可能是附近有正在蔓延的活性源石環境。", "name": "巴別塔小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，我們沒收到本艦遇襲的訊息，更何況，還有殿下本人和那位博士坐鎮呢。", "name": "巴別塔小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場仗，我們就快贏了。", "name": "巴別塔小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#8$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車在哪裡？我們馬上回去。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#11$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，我們還沒有接到下一步的行動指令。", "name": "巴別塔小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果貿然行動，有可能會打亂博士的規劃——", "name": "巴別塔小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下，W，有通訊——是Scout！", "name": "巴別塔小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Scout說……", "name": "巴別塔小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "巴別塔小隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1308_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#4$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "…………", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#6$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warchaos_intro", "key": "$warchaos_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巴別塔只是一個落腳點，和以往的任何一個都沒什麼區別，W一直是這麼以為的。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許，這裡能隨時提供乾淨的食物和水，這裡不會輕易拋棄已經失去行動力的傷患，這裡有幾個還算有趣的傢伙。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但說到底，只要能歇腳，都一樣。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和赫德雷與伊內絲一起行動之前，W已經不止一次失去過棲身之所。"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有時她回到營地，卻發現營地已經陷入一片火海，有時則是她親手點燃火苗。"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她習以為常，沒有薩卡茲真的以為自己能享受平靜與安寧，毀滅才是常態，動盪才帶來樂趣。"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，在看到倒塌的橫樑，看到走廊裡還未乾涸的血，看到吼叫著發出指令的醫生的時候——"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她發現，自己真切地感覺到了……崩塌。"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡——", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#4$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1362_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1362_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓讓，都讓開，這裡也有傷患！", "name": "巴別塔成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1362_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快，把急救室全部空出來——", "name": "巴別塔成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1362_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#4$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1362_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別擋路！", "name": "巴別塔成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1362_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下在哪裡？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1362_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道，所有安保系統都失效了，凱爾希醫生正在——等等，小心！", "name": "巴別塔成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1362_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$knifegore", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_bladeline_01_small", "roz": 137.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "無角的刺客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是你們做的？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲。", "name": "無角的刺客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經結束了。", "name": "無角的刺客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別他媽的說這種話。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing1", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing2", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.7}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing4", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.9}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 60.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_slash_cross", "y": 150.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_spark_01_mid", "y": 150.0, "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_spark_01_mid", "layer": 3.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Effect",