}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昏暗再度侵襲視野，詛咒總是難以消退。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑夜擁抱一切光芒，黑夜吞噬一切光芒，沒有人能逃得開黑夜。"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰鬥已經結束了，紛爭也已經結束了。", "name": "無角的刺客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽好了，薩卡茲，勝利者是——", "name": "無角的刺客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1307_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_knife", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_bladeline_01_large", "rox": 50.0, "roz": 50.0, "y": 100.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……唔。", "name": "無角的刺客"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一柄利刃洞穿了無角刺客的胸膛。"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W，巴別塔應該沒有向你發出任何指令，你為什麼在這裡？", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要和我談我的違規問題？現在？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dignified_intro", "key": "$dignified_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#9$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#9$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸看著她。"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W與阿斯卡綸已經共事了不短的時間，但還是第一次看到她露出這樣的表情。這個冰做的刺客……竟然也會有如此哀傷的眼神。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……阿斯卡綸，Scout說的都是真的？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不該在這個時候回來。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#2$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下在哪裡？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W，徹底掃蕩整艘船。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島還沒有擺脫危險，凱爾希醫生有緊急情況要處理，現在只能靠我們。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我問你，特蕾西婭殿下在哪裡？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#7$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要你首先前往動力層，那裡可能是他們最先潛入的位置。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#3$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 0.3, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你他媽是聾了嗎？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#3$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們說她死了，我總要見一見……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#3$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽好了，薩卡茲雇傭兵W。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#9$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你不想她的全部努力……都化為泡影，如果你不希望巴別塔就此崩塌，那就去幹你該幹的事。", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#9$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#9$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 0.8, "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 3.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "110,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#10$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈！你們這些廢物，你們全都是些廢物。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#5$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真可笑，我居然會信任你們，我居然曾經相信你們可以——", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#5$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstprun", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "什麼都沒有改變。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "到頭來，什麼都沒有改變。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他們不是很厲害嗎？這艘船上的人，一個兩個不是都很厲害嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他們不是天天都高談闊論那些了不起的願望，說著什麼遠大的理想嗎？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "他們怎麼連一個人都保護不了？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "那他們所說的那些東西，我以為的那些東西……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "說到底，真正愚蠢的人是我自己。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_dooropen", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到了。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議長室裡，只有滿地鮮血，和雜亂的腳印。"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其餘的，什麼都沒有剩下。"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就如同什麼都沒有存在過。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑暗是這麼濃稠，黑暗總是這麼濃稠。"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭殿下死了。"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我都沒能再見她一面。"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$storyendjp_intro", "key": "$storyendjp_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下？您為什麼在這……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#4$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這扇門還在這——什麼時候修好的？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#10$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，可露希爾還是有點用的嘛，總算幹了點事。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#9$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老女人也是……您走了以後，羅德島還沒走到解散的地步，她盡力了，小兔子也是。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#10$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有我……我……想要再見您。來到倫蒂尼姆之後，我就一直想著什麼時候能……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#10$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下，其實我一直挺搞不懂的，您到底為什麼一直……要讓自己這麼……這麼……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#10$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像我一直搞不懂，您為什麼，會對那扇壞掉的門那麼關心……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#11$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭，已經離開了。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#11$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那現在站著的到底是誰……不，我一定是在做夢，殿下怎麼會對我說話。我是在自言自語嗎？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#11$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可薩卡茲還有未竟的事業，我會將自己獻於這條道路。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了所有人，都可以安然入夢的那個將來。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#8$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1343_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我理解不了，但我願意相信您。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#11$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您怎麼辦……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1343_1#11$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1296_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "特蕾西婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1296_1#9$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 0.8, "loop": "false", "channel": "twalk"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.5, "channel": "twalk"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭轉過身，推開了門。"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_open_door", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "50_i02_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_marblefootsteps_loop", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "twalk"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "twalk", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 3.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.7, "amount": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "門打開了。"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭邁開腳步，無數身影跟隨在她的身後。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的聲音迴盪著，他們的聲音尖嘯著。"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“薩卡茲不會被拯救。”"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“無人能逃離苦難，因為我們曾經苦難。無人能擺脫憎恨，因為我們曾經憎恨。”"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“所有無意義的死亡，所有被浪費的希望……樂園何在？安寧何在？”"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭的腳步如此沉重，如此緩慢。"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W張了張嘴，她該說什麼呢？她又能說什麼呢？"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她終於意識到，剛才發生的並非對話，只是殿下留下的一些殘響。"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可她還是忍不住，向那個身影發問。"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下，如果您還活著，我該怎麼做才能拯救您？", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續向前走吧，你們會走到比我更遠的地方。", "name": "特蕾西婭"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼才算走得更遠……？", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我殺了你，就可以拯救你嗎？", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有回答。"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭沒有回頭，那些身影也沒有回頭。"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕他們的腳步是如此緩慢，他們的方向卻從未改變。"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭的身影漸行漸遠。"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "50_i02_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下！", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "壓抑已久的聲音終於喊出。"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去他媽的眾魂，去他媽的苦難。", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會為您重新找回平靜。不，也許殿下您從沒獲得真正的……可是——啊啊！管他的！", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把這些……結束吧。", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下，我會把這些結束的。", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"channel": "twalk", "volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.2}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"channel": "twalk", "volume": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭的腳步是不是停下了一瞬呢，W不能確定。"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "50_i02_3", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "twalk", "fadetime": 5.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的身影漸漸朦朧，溶化，消失在了一片光芒之中。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑暗再次襲來。"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g6_sarkazancientruins", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是，什麼？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1332_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽到了，那位魔王留下的殘響。", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#3$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還活著——！", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#11$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喀利喀的身影不知何時出現在了W的身後，炸彈與落石依舊沒有在他身上留下痕跡。"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他走到W身邊，緩緩闔上了那扇門。"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位殿下已經遠去。", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我炸了你的老巢，你竟然還這麼心平氣和？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#13$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳舊的遺跡，終歸塵土，何時損毀並無區別。", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還真是豁達——有意思，我得承認我開始對你有點興趣了。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是很厲害嗎？那之前一個個魔王就沒人想派你去幹點更有用的事？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我侍奉的殿下……奎薩圖什塔，超越歷史的雄主，在時間的長河中，他如同巨人。", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我追隨他征戰，我的兵刃供他驅使，這副身軀，也本該用於延續他的生命。", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，看來不管多麼瘋魔的傢伙，都有幾個忠心耿耿的擁護者啊。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實驗失敗了，我未能延續自己的使命，只得將自己流放。", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無用之人，只能收集那些英雄的殘片存放各處，憑弔過去。", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1332_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我始終在等待……一個推開未來之門的人。", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#3$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1332_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾經以為，那個人會是特蕾西婭。", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#2$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身形瘦削的人拾起地上破碎的祭壇殘片，將它碾為細碎的粉末。隨即，用沾滿了暗淡粉末的手指，沿著面頰深深抹下。"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就如同在臉上留下了一道淚痕。"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特蕾西婭殿下已經遠去，她最後的殘響由你拾起。", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "魔王的舊部，年輕的薩卡茲。你出現在這裡，未必是巧合。", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#1$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯哼，我也這麼覺得。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摸到了赦罪師的老巢，怎麼也得留點東西才行啊。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$exciting_intro", "key": "$exciting_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喀利喀低下頭，不知何時，數枚炸彈已經安置在他腳下。"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1332_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你為何……", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#3$1"}, {"id": 450, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不得不說，在我認識的老傢伙裡，你還算比較有趣的一個。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1"}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但作為和赦罪師有關的人，我還是得給你留點“禮物”才行。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1332_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傭兵，你叫什麼名字？", "name": "喀利喀"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1332_1#3$1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去特雷西斯的墓碑上找吧。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#14$1"}, {"id": 457, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_explosion", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}